sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI
    participant Pager
    participant Agent
    participant Hooks
    participant Sandbox
    participant Memory
    participant LLM

    User->>CLI: Request
    CLI->>Pager: Route
    Pager->>Agent: Process

    Agent->>Hooks: Pre-Request
    Hooks-->>Agent: Allowed/Denied

    loop Agent Loop
        Agent->>LLM: Send to Model
        LLM-->>Agent: Response

        alt Tool Call
            Agent->>Sandbox: Execute Tool
            Sandbox-->>Agent: Tool Result
            Agent->>Hooks: Post-Tool
        end

        Agent->>Memory: Retrieve Context
        Memory-->>Agent: Context
    end

    Agent->>LLM: Build Prompt
    LLM-->>Agent: Compaction Result

    Agent->>Memory: Update Session
    Agent->>Pager: Render Response
    Pager-->>User: Display